  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Class</p><p>Prerequisite: At least 14+ levels in Cooking Nin. </p><p><br />You have learnt how to use the chakra inside your snacks to power your own snacks, allowing your own snacks to work as a sort of catalyst for your jutsu. </p><p><br />• When you cast a jutsu, you can spend one snack to reduce the cost of the jutsu by 1/4 rounded down. <br />you can spend 4 snacks to reduce the cost by 1/3rd rounded down, and lastly you can spend 6 snacks to reduce the cost by 1/2 rounded down.</p>",
